00:05:15.200 --> 00:05:16.690
YOSSI ELKRIEF: Sounds
good to me.

00:05:16.690 --> 00:05:18.910
RICH HYNDMAN: Really not too
hard to implement at all.

00:05:18.910 --> 00:05:20.830
