imagery.

00:05:31.330 --> 00:05:33.720
You can have traffic data.

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:35.120
You can do animations.

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:36.960
You can give the camera a new
location and tell it to

00:05:36.960 --> 00:05:39.160
animate to it, or a
new zoom level.

00:05:39.160 --> 00:05:39.600
[INAUDIBLE]

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:41.590
