done that once,

00:05:47.840 --> 00:05:48.845
it's not too bad.

00:05:48.845 --> 00:05:53.630
Just go to the API's console
and turn on Google Maps API

00:05:53.630 --> 00:05:56.260
version [? 2 ?] for Android in
services, and then you can

00:05:56.260 --> 00:05:58.800
create your own new Android
application, and off you go.

